Conflict matrix or Not

Source: R/CFmatrixParse.R
isCFM.Rd

A logical return, TRUE for conflict free.

isCFM(CFmatrix_file)

Arguments

CFmatrix_file

a file path to CFMatrix file.

Value

a bool value

Examples

CFmatrix_file = system.file("extdata", "ground_truth_tree.CFMatrix", package = "converTree")
isCFM(CFmatrix_file)
#> [1] TRUE
